        "text": "# Best Angel Investors in the World\n\nHere are some of the most successful and influential angel investors globally:\n\n## Top-Tier Angel Investors\n\n### **1. Marc Andreessen**\nCo-founder of [Andreessen Horowitz](https://a16z.com/) and creator of Netscape. Early investments include Facebook, Twitter, Airbnb, and Pinterest.\n\n### **2. Peter Thiel**\nCo-founder of [PayPal](https://www.paypal.com/) and [Palantir Technologies](https://www.palantir.com/). Famous for being Facebook's first outside investor ($500K for 10.2% stake in 2004). Also founded [Founders Fund](https://foundersfund.com/).\n\n### **3. Reid Hoffman**\nCo-founder of [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/). Early investor in Facebook, Airbnb, and numerous other startups through [Greylock Partners](https://greylock.com/).\n\n### **4. Naval Ravikant**\nFounder of [AngelList](https://www.angellist.com/), which revolutionized angel investing. Early investments include Twitter, Uber, and Postmates.\n\n### **5. Elad Gil**\nFormer Google executive and investor in Airbnb, Coinbase, Instacart, Pinterest, Square, and Stripe. Author of [\"High Growth Handbook\"](http://growth.eladgil.com/).\n\n### **6. Chris Sacca**\nFounder of [Lowercase Capital](https://lowercasecapital.com/). Early investor in Twitter, Uber, Instagram, and Kickstarter.\n\n### **7. Ron Conway**\nFounder of [SV Angel](https://svangel.com/). Known as the \"Godfather of Silicon Valley\" with investments in Google, Facebook, Twitter, Airbnb, and Pinterest.\n\n### **8. Esther Dyson**\nTechnology journalist and investor through [Wellville](https://wellville.net/). Early investor in Flickr, del.icio.us, and numerous health tech companies.\n\n### **9. Jason Calacanis**\nFounder of [LAUNCH](https://www.launch.co/). Early investor in Uber, Robinhood, and Calm. Hosts the [All-In Podcast](https://www.allinpodcast.co/).\n\n### **10. Jeff Bezos (through Bezos Expeditions)**\nAmazon founder who has made angel investments through [Bezos Expeditions](https://www.crunchbase.com/organization/bezos-expeditions) in companies like Airbnb, Twitter, and Google.\n\n## Notable International Angel Investors\n\n### **11. Yuri Milner**\nFounder of [DST Global](https://www.dst-global.com/). Early investor in Facebook, Twitter, Airbnb, and Spotify.\n\n### **12. Li Ka-shing**\nHong Kong billionaire who invests through [Horizons Ventures](https://www.horizonsventures.com/). Portfolio includes Facebook, Spotify, and Zoom.\n\n### **13. Chamath Palihapitiya**\nFounder of [Social Capital](https://www.socialcapital.com/). Former Facebook executive with investments in Slack, Box, and Yammer.\n\n## Resources for Learning More\n\n- [AngelList](https://www.angellist.com/) - Platform to track angel investors and their portfolios\n- [Crunchbase](https://www.crunchbase.com/) - Database of investors and their investment history\n- [Forbes Midas List](https://www.forbes.com/midas/) - Annual ranking of top tech investors\n- [CB Insights](https://www.cbinsights.com/) - Research on top investors and venture capital trends\n\nThese investors are known for their track records, the quality of companies they've backed, and their ability to add strategic value beyond just capital.",
